Class Message

java.lang.Object
  core.messages.Message
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Message
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Object read and written in the Socket for communication is paremetrized with the owner of the message, the destination, the type of message, the input type (when Type is COMMAND), if it's urgent, and id for the message, and the contents
